source: TEXT_HEAVNZ505_01840_SEQ_00<tab>Mogmill looks like he's daydreaming─or not, it's hard to tell.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ505_01840_SEQ_00<tab>Mogmill a l'air fasciné par quelque chose.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ505_01840_SEQ_01<tab>Mogmill, always thinking about where to get his paws on the next piece of landlord treasure, has recruited you to go to the House of Letters and look for shiny objects. He assures you that all the other moogles go to Tharl Oom Khash, so there should be plenty lying around. Go to the House of Letters and collect five shiny objects of dubious value.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ505_01840_SEQ_01<tab>Mogmill vous a parlé de la fascination des Mogs pour les métaux miroitants forgés par les humains. Il vous a révélé qu'on pouvait trouver des <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E8AEC0302 /var> dans les <var 33 ((EObj)) 0DF61E9AD50302 /var> de la Maison des lettreux, et il vous a demandé d'aller lui en chercher cinq en échange de cette information.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ505_01840_SEQ_02<tab>You have obtained five shiny spillikins, and although they are shiny, you fail to see any practical value. Return to Moghome and deliver them to Mogmill─maybe he will put them to better use.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ505_01840_SEQ_02<tab>Vous avez trouvé cinq <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E8AEC0302 /var>. Apportez-les à Mogmill près du Nid-Mog.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ505_01840_SEQ_03<tab>Mogmill is thrilled at the objects you deliver to him, and is one step closer to having the largest collection of shiny, useless objects out of any moogle from Moghome.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ505_01840_SEQ_03<tab>Mogmill était ravi du cadeau que vous lui avez fait, persuadé que les autres Mogs seraient jaloux de tels <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E8AEC0302 /var>, et il vous a demandé de garder ce petit secret pour vous.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ505_01840_TODO_01<tab>Deliver the sparkly spillikins to Mogmill.

TEXT_HEAVNZ505_01840_MOGMILL_000_000<tab>The shiny sundries made by the landlords are in vogue all across Moghome, kupo! But, moogles can't work metal themselves, so everyone goes searching for shiny objects at Tharl Oom Khash.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ505_01840_MOGMILL_000_000<tab>Vous savez, on adore les métaux miroitants forgés par les humains, kuppo<var 1D /var>! Mal<var 16 /var>heu<var 16 /var>reu<var 16 /var>se<var 16 /var>ment, on ne sait pas comment les imiter... C'est pour ça qu'on va généralement en ramasser à Tharl Oom Khash. Mais... Hmm...

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ505_01840_MOGMILL_000_001<tab>But <var 1A 02 /var>I<var 1A 01 /var> know a secret place─the House of Letters, kupo! So many shiny objects are just waiting for someone adventurous to go pick them up. And they <var 1A 02 /var>do<var 1A 01 /var> call you an adventurer, so... What do you say? If I had five sparkling objects, that should be enough to make the other moogles jealous!
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ505_01840_MOGMILL_000_001<tab>Allez, je peux bien vous dire un secret, à vous<var 1D /var>! À la Maison des lettreux, il y a des <var 33 ((EObj)) 0DF61E9AD50302 /var> qui contiennent des <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E8AEC0302 /var><var 1D /var>! Une telle info mérite bien que vous alliez m'en chercher quelques-uns, non<var 1D /var>? Disons cinq<var 1D /var>! Vous me feriez vraiment plaisir, kuppo<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ505_01840_MOGMILL_000_010<tab>Don't tell anyone, but treasures litter the House of Letters. All I need you to do is bring me five of them and it'll make all the other moogles jealous!
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ505_01840_MOGMILL_000_010<tab>Vous voulez bien aller me chercher cinq <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E8AEC0302 /var> dans les <var 33 ((EObj)) 0DF61E9AD50302 /var> de la Maison des lettreux<var 1D /var>? Vous me feriez vraiment plaisir, kuppo<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ505_01840_MOGMILL_000_020<tab>I can't believe no one has thought to go look there yet... Ah, adventurer, were you able to find enough of the landlords' shiny objects?
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ505_01840_MOGMILL_000_020<tab>Alors<var 1D /var>! Est-ce que vous avez trouvé cinq <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E8AEC0302 /var> dans les <var 33 ((EObj)) 0DF61E9AD50302 /var> de la Maison des lettreux, kuppo<var 1D /var>!?

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ505_01840_MOGMILL_000_021<tab>Wonderful! Amazing! Spectacular, kupopo! I've never seen such lustrous objects before! I'll be the talk of Moghome before long. Remember, adventurer, the House of Letters is our little secret!
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ505_01840_MOGMILL_000_021<tab>Ouaaah<var 1D /var>! Ils sont vraiment magnifiques<var 1D /var>! Merci beaucoup<var 1D /var>! Les autres vont être tellement jaloux<var 1D /var>! Mais chuuut<var 1D /var>! Ne dites à personne où vous les avez trouvés. Ce sera notre petit secret, kuppo<var 1D /var>!
